sequenceDiagram
    participant Auto as auto.ts
    participant Lock as crash-recovery.ts
    participant OS as session-lock.ts (flock)
    participant Forensics as session-forensics.ts
    participant User as 用户终端

    Auto->>OS: acquireLock(basePath)
    OS-->>Auto: 互斥锁获取成功
    Auto->>Lock: writeLock(basePath, unitType, unitId, sessionFile)
    Note over Lock: 写入 .gsd/runtime/auto.lock
    Auto->>Auto: 执行 Unit（可能崩溃）
    Note over Auto,Lock: 进程崩溃，锁文件未删除

    Auto->>Lock: detectCrash(basePath)
    Lock->>Lock: 读取锁文件，检查 PID 是否存活
    Lock-->>Auto: {crashed: true, unitType, sessionFile}
    Auto->>Forensics: synthesizeCrashRecovery(sessionFile)
    Forensics->>Forensics: 解析 JSONL，提取已完成工具调用
    Forensics-->>Auto: 崩溃摘要
    Auto->>User: "上次在执行 execute-task 时崩溃，是否继续？"